{"id":142392,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/图辑：日本天皇探访地震灾民/","date":"2011-04-01T12:01:01Z","modified":"2011-04-01T12:01:01Z","title":"图辑：日本天皇探访地震灾民","content":"<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/30/110330142433_japan1_926x521_reuters.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"日本天皇明仁和皇后美智子\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/30/110330142433_japan1_926x521_reuters.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>日本天皇明仁和皇后美智子周三（3月30日）前往东京武道馆，探望那里安置的大地震灾民。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/30/110330142609_japan2_926x521_ap_nocredit.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"日本天皇明仁和皇后美智子\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/30/110330142609_japan2_926x521_ap_nocredit.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>东京武道馆内安置大约300名灾民，绝大多数来自受地震海啸和核电站危机影响的福岛县。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/30/110330142817_japan3_926x521_ap.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"日本天皇明仁和皇后美智子\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/30/110330142817_japan3_926x521_ap.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>有些灾民见到天皇很激动，对他的探访表示感谢。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/30/110330143127_japan4_926x521_ap.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"日本天皇明仁和皇后美智子\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/30/110330143127_japan4_926x521_ap.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>日本天皇希望以后有机会前往灾区探访。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/30/110330143353_japan5_926x521_ap.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"日本天皇明仁和皇后美智子探访灾民\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/30/110330143353_japan5_926x521_ap.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>发生在3月11日的大地震，导致1万1千多人死亡，至今仍有很多人无家可归。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/30/110330143612_japan6_926x521_ap.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"日本明仁天皇\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/30/110330143612_japan6_926x521_ap.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>发生大地震后，明仁天皇曾经在3月16日发表全国电视讲话，呼吁团结一致共渡艰难。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n</ul></div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/ASQVFZ15XYHD9VeAciaL0qo4J8E/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/ASQVFZ15XYHD9VeAciaL0qo4J8E/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/ASQVFZ15XYHD9VeAciaL0qo4J8E/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/ASQVFZ15XYHD9VeAciaL0qo4J8E/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/BBC/World/~4/ihn0cV60bfY\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><b>要翻墙？(发邮件到Gmail):fanqiang70maATgmail.com</b></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[9826,15660]}